  <h3>
    Instructions
  </h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Quests will require you to find a certain answer that you will enter into the answer tab.</li>
    <li>The task will be only marked complete if it is correct. </li>
    <li>Quests are split up into 4 different zones.</li>
    <li>Each task has a different value so try to complete all.</li>
    <li>Quests or move onto the next task, if you feel the need.</li>
    <li>The bonus task is worth the most points but can also be the most time consuming/challenging.</li>
    <li>The duration of the scavenger hunt is 4 hours.</li>
    <li>Once the timer is up please make your way to the
    final checkpoint to see which team has won!</li>
  </ul>

  <a name="#rules"></a>
  <h3>
    Rules
  </h3>
  <ul>
  <li>Teams must stick together. If spotted apart, teams will be disqualified.</li>
  <li>Yes, we will be watching.</li>
  <li>You can’t share your answers with other teams. Or do, if you don’t want to win.</li>
  <li>If multiple teams have completed all Quests, the team that completes all
    Quests quickest wins.</li>
  </ul>

